CustomField.description: Monthly fee on-line transmission and background maps from abroad within the EU and selected European countries from one unit. It's about European countries that do not belong to the EU - Ukraine, Russia, Turkey, Belorussia, Switzerland, Montenegro, Serbia, Albania. Does not contain an SMS with a location request. This service is an additional service to tariffs EU 24 and EU 36.
